                <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
              </msItem>
                <msItem xml:id="ms_i8"><locus from="63v" to="65v"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT3083RepCh363"/><incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘብርሃናት፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘሥልጣናት፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘአርእስተ፡ መላእክት፡ ዘእምታሕተ፡ እኂዞትከ። ኵሉ፡ ፍጥረት፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
              </msItem>
                <msItem xml:id="ms_i9"><locus from="66r" to="68v"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT1190Baenta"/><incipit xml:lang="gez">በእንተ፡ ቅድሳት፡ ሰላማዊት፡ ናስስተበቍዕ፡ (sic) ከመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ያስተሣልመነ፡ በሣህለ፡ ዚአሁ። <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
